==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: male chauvinism
<hw>male chauvinism</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>Disparaging, patronizing,
discriminatory or abusive speech or behavior by males toward females
stemming from a belief that males are superior to females and females
therefore worthy of less respect and inferior treatment. A form of
<isa>sexism</isa>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>male chauvinist</ent>⟦br⟧
